      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n   1. The applicant should be a resident of Haryana.\n   1. The applicant should belong to the Scheduled Caste Category.\n   1. The applicant should belong to the Below Poverty Line (BPL) family.\n   1. The applicant&amp;#39;s annual family income should not exceed ₹1,80,000/- in both rural and urban areas.\n   1. The applicant&amp;#39;s annual family income should not exceed the BPL limit.\n   1. The applicant&amp;#39;s name should be included in the BPL Survey List.\n\n**Note:** The eligibility of the applicant is verified by the field staff before sponsoring the same to the bank for sanction.\n",
